Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.47,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眩しい風のなかで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:37.56,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描くよ　君の笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:43.35,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}素直になれる瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:46.77,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小さなことで揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:50.37,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}弱い自分が悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:54.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泣きたいときだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:56.28,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}上を向いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:03:01.96,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}わたしだけにできることがあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:10.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あきらめないよ　君を守り続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:16.57,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}とまらないスピードで想いがあふれていく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}負けたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:22.82,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰よりも輝いていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}星がみえない日も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光はある　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じること…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:35.01,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い、　未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:42.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの空で逢えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================opcn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.47,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}炫目的風中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:37.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描繪你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:43.35,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}變得坦率的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:46.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因小事而動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:50.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}軟弱的自己令我懊惱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:54.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:56.28,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也仰頭忍淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:03:01.96,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}必定有唯有我能做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:10.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永不言棄 一直守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:16.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思念正以停不下的速度膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不想認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:22.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願比任何人都耀目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使夜空沒有繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}亦會有光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:31.97,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:35.01,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}前往未來的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:42.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}能在那片天空相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================zhengwen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\bord2\blur4\pos(430,285)\fs26\1c&HE4E4E4&\3c&H2D2D2D&}插班生是第二個青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 現在我們進行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS基本飛行操縱的實踐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑 奧魯戈多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們試飛一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟練的IS操縱者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開IS用不了1秒鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 白式!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 飛!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:00:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規格上說 白式的推進力更勝一籌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要「想像自己前方展開個三角錐」來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像終歸是想像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸索適合自己的方法更有建設性哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實飛在天上的感覺 還是很模糊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.63,0:01:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這機體為什麼會浮在空中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話 放學後可以指導一下你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時 我們單獨…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑 奥魯戈多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試急速降落和完全停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真熟練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 還以為要死翹翹了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨 竟然在操場撞出個大坑來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太丢臉了 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教你的還沒記…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥「一夏」?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過保險起見 還是去趟保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝備了IS 怎麼可能受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 篠之之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心別人是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有臉說 裝乖女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比心腸狠毒的要強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們倆…怎麼關係這麼差
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是IS學園
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑 恭喜你當上班級代表～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥是我當班級代表
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我退出了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過想了想 這結果也是理所當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟對手是我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我也反省了一下自己太孩子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定讓位給一夏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉亞真懂事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 難得有個男生 得捧一捧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受歡迎啊 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真這麼認為?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是新聞部的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 塞西莉亞也一起拍個照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照我們倆麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.77,0:06:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是引人注目的專用機擁有者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能握個手啥的就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 拍下的照片 我能拿一份是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 請兩位握手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 給點笑容靠近點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼全部人都擠進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓你偷跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛 今天很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得累
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換作你會開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還真開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在要換睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背過身去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我刷牙那時換不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 腰帶換新的了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀察得真仔細
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都看著你 當然會發現啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 每天都看著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 耍脾氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我沒放心上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到班級對抗戰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 有沒聽說2班換了代表
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好像換給了個插班生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,插班生? 現在才轉過來?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 聽說是中國來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 現在才認為我有威脅 派人轉過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知是個怎樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強不強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前擁有專用機的 只有1班和4班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的消息太落後了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2班的班級代表 現在也是專用機擁有者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想赢就沒這麼輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是鈴?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 中國代表候補生 凰鈴音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天過來向你們宣戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是2班的插班生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中國的代表候補生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她 她是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像跟一夏關係很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝什麼呢 一點都不適合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:09:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到短班會的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千 千冬姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫織斑老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊回去 別擋路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過後再來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑啊 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是代表候補生…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳 你竟然是2班的插班生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先通知我一聲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做再會就沒驚喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是很怕千冬姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才 才沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅長應付她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那麼喜歡吃拉麵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好一年沒見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當 當然好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你 偶爾也生個病受個傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼願望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 你啥時候當代表候補生了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想間你呢 看到新聞嚇了我一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒想到自己會進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你入學考試開動了IS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.75,0:11:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我入學考試的考場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是市立多功能大禮堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在裡面迷了路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問了職員 他們也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉了很多地方後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IS?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能開動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你 不能進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有反應?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能 男人竟然能開動IS?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就進來這學園了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 趕緊說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是跟她在交交交交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我我我才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我們只是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅竹馬?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛走 她就轉進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篠之之箒 之前也跟你提過的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箒是第一個青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是第二個了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 以後多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了我也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫塞西莉亞·奧魯戈多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英國的代表候補生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天才跟一夏決鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你當了1班的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 為勢所逼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要麼我指導你練習IS的操縱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有聽人說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口氣真大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責教一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是2班的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要敵人的施捨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在跟一夏聊著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無關人員請到一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你 後來的還這麼厚臉皮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是後來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他打交道的時間比你長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這麼說 我是最早的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏經常到我家吃飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏整天都來我家吃飯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小學開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒聽說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是經常去鈴家開的中餐館
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 只是下館子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下館子的話 倒是沒什麼不自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 應該挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 放學見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你那邊練習完了我再過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要空出時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篠之之 你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經批准了我用訓練機了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始 我要陪他特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「打鐵」…是日本的量產型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然這麼爽快地批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 一夏 我們開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來當一夏的教練
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 一夏 開始練習
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當你教練 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 叫你平常不鍛煉 累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二對一啊 小姐 不累才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 過後見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也回房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暫時還動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你沒轍 那我先去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到班級對抗賽這段時間 一直都這樣練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝運動飲料沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你一直在等我?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算剩我們倆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在是不是很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少了個玩伴 多少也會寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:17:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼久沒見 不是有很多話要說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 忘了件很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有跟初中時的朋友聯繫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到你回來 肯定會超開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個 比如說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 身子有點涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箒也差不多洗完澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箒是剛才那女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟她是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是青梅竹馬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第二個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅竹馬跟洗澡有什麼關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在跟她住一個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是房間沒準備好 所以就住一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是你跟她同吃同住了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 幸虧是跟她住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不認識的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會緊張到睡眠不足的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是青梅竹馬就行了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 只要是青梅竹馬就行了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是啊 跟我換個房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥我要跟你換
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 篠之之也不想跟男生住一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我也沒說不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 這是我跟一夏的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我也是他的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我不會換房間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回你自己房間去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得我們的約定麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 小學那時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別無視我!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分展開…好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那下 要是普通人就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 剛才說到約定啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該…還記得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 是那個麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你廚藝好了 每天都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都請我吃咕嚕肉是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是說每天都請我吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 對我這一個人住的來說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是天大的好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差勁!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然記不好跟女生的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種男人要不得!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著被狗咬死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是記得好好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定的意思不同啊 意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說明一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說 說明…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼好開口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周的班級對抗戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了的要聽赢了的一個命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了你就要說明白了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我做好心理準備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被馬踹死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一戰就是對鈴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方IS叫「甲龍」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟織斑的白式一樣 都是近戰型
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟對我那時 情況不一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張 按練習那時來應該能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那個打中 估計很痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請雙方移動至規定位置
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在道歉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以稍微減輕你的痛苦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 全力放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先說一句 絕對防禦並不是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有能突破護盾的攻擊力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能將人殺個半死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:22:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方請開始比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.18,0:23:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於開幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.43,0:23:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織斑跟凰鈴音的對決
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互間使盡秘訣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.93,0:23:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行死鬥 激鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.27,0:23:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對方是第三世代兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白式是否有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 織斑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家看到男子漢的骨氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.78,0:24:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,325)\fs16}（league Match）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.78,0:24:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集決戰! 班級對抗戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.86,0:24:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別錯過意外的結局哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.95,0:24:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然草字頭「萌」很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但熊熊烈火的「燃」也很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================zhengwen2
